00:16:00,000 --> 00:16:02,000
 There's no question that thing could have swallowed me up.

255
00:16:02,000 --> 00:16:03,000
 Now here's the question.

256
00:16:03,000 --> 00:16:07,000
 If a whale swallowed a man whole, by the way, they found a whale not many years ago

257
00:16:07,000 --> 00:16:13,000
 that had swallowed a 450-pound giant squid whole.

258
00:16:13,000 --> 00:16:15,000
 450 pounds.

259
00:16:15,000 --> 00:16:20,000
 And it was later killed, that particular whale, and it was not yet digested.

